{"tid":2454910,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"央視統戰新節目　《台海之聲》對台灣喊:「用最熟悉的鄉音與海峽對岸的骨肉天親道一聲晚安。」","createTime":"2021-03-20T15:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T15:29:23.000Z","uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fc096672313c9e9a7f7ae95b7ce54f7ee4e20eab","tid":2454910,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T15:15:28.000Z","msg":"中國對台統戰動作不斷，今天又發佈消息指，央視旗下電台節目《台海之聲》即將開播，特別宣傳有關收聽頻率、節目片頭曲與片尾曲等相關內容，當中提及福州和馬祖地區共享一頻道；廈門和金門則使用另一頻道。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，《台海之聲》開始與結束樂曲分別為鋼琴版《明月千里寄相思》與小提琴版《在銀色月光下》，男女播音員會用國語、閩南話、客家話三種語言廣播。央視宣傳稱，節目「聲音穿越海峽，共話兩岸一家」。宣傳詞句還相當肉麻地寫著「用最熟悉的鄉音與海峽對岸的骨肉天親道一聲晚安。」（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"d7d37b9c99ffbf19f1e1ae7d10175b8d86e310a9","tid":2454910,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T15:17:20.000Z","msg":"中共版美國之音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f23c89ac838f3b61a395547eeca4980e85afee","tid":2454910,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T15:17:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210320/TO5MSDMVEFHCTGWE27D3UABC6M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210320%2FTO5MSDMVEFHCTGWE27D3UABC6M%2F&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDJq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=636b0a10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210320%2FTO5MSDMVEFHCTGWE27D3UABC6M%2F&h=93850f61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210320/TO5MSDMVEFHCTGWE27D3UABC6M/</a>"},{"pid":"4e61cce46c7ddca6b99d3573d1d20ebebf554634","tid":2454910,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7d37b9c99ffbf19f1e1ae7d10175b8d86e310a9","tid":2454910,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T15:17:20.000Z","msg":"中共版美國之音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T15:18